videos.headline: Penn State RB finds a hole and takes it in for first TD
videos.description: Nittany Lions RB Journey Brown exploits the defense taking advantage of the open field and runs it in for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Slade muscles through to increase Penn State's lead
videos.description: Penn State RB Ricky Slade punches through the defense to put the Nittany Lions up 20-0.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Slade muscles through to increase Penn State's lead) 2019/08/31 ESHEET

videos.headline: Penn State QB takes big hit, still delivers 36-yard touchdown
videos.description: Nittany Lions QB Sean Clifford delivers after being taken down on a 36-yard touchdown pass to KJ Hamler to put Penn State up 27-0.
